@host = http://localhost:4000/api

### Health
GET {{host}}/health

### Overview (default range Apr 2025 → Feb 2026)
GET {{host}}/finance/overview

### Overview narrowed to a single month
GET {{host}}/finance/overview?dateRange=2025-09-01:2025-09-30

### KPIs only
GET {{host}}/finance/kpis

### Forex — last week (default)
GET {{host}}/finance/forex

### Forex — month view
GET {{host}}/finance/forex?range=month

### Revenue — all ports
GET {{host}}/finance/revenue

### Revenue — single port + date range
GET {{host}}/finance/revenue?port=Hazira&dateRange=2025-10-01:2025-12-31

### Working capital
GET {{host}}/finance/working-capital

### Profitability — port wise (default mode)
GET {{host}}/finance/profitability

### Profitability — segment wise
GET {{host}}/finance/profitability?mode=segment

### Profitability — segment wise, filtered
GET {{host}}/finance/profitability?mode=segment&segment=SNS&dateRange=2025-06-01:2025-08-31

### Sales overview
GET {{host}}/finance/sales

### Filters
GET {{host}}/filters/ports

###
GET {{host}}/filters/segments

###
GET {{host}}/filters/zones

### Validation error example (malformed dateRange)
GET {{host}}/finance/overview?dateRange=garbage
